{"tid":2277321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"天水圍5歲唐狗疑遭虐殺 兇案現場血迹斑斑　","createTime":"2020-11-08T11:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T12:54:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f18c37c80fd2a7d18d395e7e058fa14aa53fea0b","tid":2277321,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"本港連日發生虐待動物案件，受害者包括貓狗及野豬，今日（8日）凌晨天水圍又再發生懷疑虐狗案，是連續4日第4宗。沙江圍一村屋住所，一隻5歲黑色唐狗被發現在屋外離奇慘死，狗主回家赫見唐狗伏屍屋外一角，地下及牆身血迹斑斑，尤如屠房，懷疑愛犬遭虐殺報警。狗主對愛犬猝逝十分心痛，形容虐待動物行為恐怖、殘忍，呼籲其他動物主人小心看顧寵物，不希望同類事件再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑被虐殺的唐狗叫「肥仔」，20歲狗主黃小姐向《蘋果》稱，昨傍晚時分，一家人外出晚飯，至晚上11時許曾折返家中取物品再次外出，當時見「肥仔」仍然精靈，並無異樣。約1.5小時後即今日凌晨1時許，一家人返家發現「肥仔」伏在屋外一角，地上及牆身滿佈血迹，黃小姐被眼前畫面嚇呆，上前查看「肥仔」已氣絕身亡，但身體仍暖。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐稱，由於住所附近約半個月前曾有兩個單位被爆竊，未知是否再有賊匪向「肥仔」狠下毒手，於是於凌晨3時報警。警員接報到場，經初步調查，將案列殘酷對待動物，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第七隊調查，暫未有人被捕。狗屍稍後由愛護動物協會撿走檢驗。黃小姐稱，愛協人員初步檢視「肥仔」無表面傷痕，懷疑被人毒殺，但要驗屍才可確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201108/FHYEET6VNRC4JG2M6BLAT6HZ3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201108%2FFHYEET6VNRC4JG2M6BLAT6HZ3U%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7wRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=371382ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201108%2FFHYEET6VNRC4JG2M6BLAT6HZ3U%2F&h=6f16b03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201108/FHYEET6VNRC4JG2M6BLAT6HZ3U/</a>"},{"pid":"4cfa2418509606ac7af1dfc2255ad945837d333c","tid":2277321,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"謎底已經解開 一定係老衲"},{"pid":"84ed8b1d3fccf2a978e80adda3be6ff0b35cf701","tid":2277321,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"而家支那係咁送D賤畜支那豬落黎<br />\n大家以後等食狗肉都得"},{"pid":"a31cd11abfda3078c2fd955ab55da338bccd4472","tid":2277321,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7838c830a4999140a7640969db8fdae935314e","tid":2277321,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"大波華：無證據，唔告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cf52ec0608676b500dd1cf5b1d454217e063e8","tid":2277321,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7838c830a4999140a7640969db8fdae935314e","tid":2277321,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"大波華：無證據，唔告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"你錯喇 ! 係唻自首, 都唔告啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}